    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/aded62ac9c354b54b39ef7090930ef6f.avif?t=1748596530\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>《Mari &amp; Bayu: The Road Home》是一款2D合作冒险游戏，你将帮助陷入迷途的Mari回到家园，与她的哥哥Tom重聚。Bayu是Mari的好朋友，他必须鼓足勇气去找回被绑架的家人，并帮助Mari恢复自信，去找到回家的路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/5ef3c1f09d8758201ed979b7a7002553.avif?t=1748596530\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>沉浸入一个在陷入迷途后重新找回自我的感人故事。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>小世界，大冒险——解开谜题、搭乘羽毛随风翱翔，骑上蚱蜢，和其他昆虫互动，利用Bayu的风之力，巧用周围环境。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/32a64c7a4d5ae97cc18ed0a58e886d7c.poster.avif?t=1748596530\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/32a64c7a4d5ae97cc18ed0a58e886d7c.webm?t=1748596530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/32a64c7a4d5ae97cc18ed0a58e886d7c.mp4?t=1748596530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>单人游玩或双人合作——你可以在单人模式中同时操纵Mari和Bayu，或者在双人合作模式中各自选其中一个。两种游戏方式都充满乐趣，各有特点。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/07b11d30f010ce7dbd9146c2019459d4.poster.avif?t=1748596530\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/07b11d30f010ce7dbd9146c2019459d4.webm?t=1748596530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/07b11d30f010ce7dbd9146c2019459d4.mp4?t=1748596530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>令人惊叹的2D美术——《Mari &amp; Bayu: The Road Home》将古典艺术与游戏引擎相结合，缔造出充满生命力，与玩家亲密互动的游戏世界。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/784c4bf2f337cc59159631b1d8dcaa9f.poster.avif?t=1748596530\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/784c4bf2f337cc59159631b1d8dcaa9f.webm?t=1748596530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/784c4bf2f337cc59159631b1d8dcaa9f.mp4?t=1748596530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>丰富独特的游戏环境——从一只蚂蚁的视角去体验世界。人类每个漫不经心的脚步，对昆虫而言都意味着一场生死攸关的冒险。深水潭、苍蝇拍、垃圾堆……那些怪物更是等不及要消灭你。游戏包含12个各不相同的独特设定。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/d25a64f4854804b8648b198318b1ed66.poster.avif?t=1748596530\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/d25a64f4854804b8648b198318b1ed66.webm?t=1748596530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725350/extras/d25a64f4854804b8648b198318b1ed66.mp4?t=1748596530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>充满大冒险的小世界等你来探索！你能最终回到家园吗？",
